    <summary>Typeless - AI voice dictation that turns natural speech into polished, ready-to-send writing across every Windows app.</summary>
    <description>Typeless is an AI voice dictation app for Windows. You speak naturally and it produces finished text - messages, emails, and documents that read as if they had been carefully typed - in real time, in whatever application you are currently writing in.

## Main features

- **Works everywhere you write** - dictate into any Windows application, not just a dedicated editor window.
- **Cleans up speech automatically** - removes filler words ("um", "uh", "you know") and unnecessary repetition.
- **Follows your corrections** - when you change your mind mid-sentence, it keeps only the final intended wording instead of transcribing both attempts.
- **Auto-formats** - spoken lists, steps, and key points come out as structured text.
- **Adapts to your style** - matches your tone and phrasing over time, and a personal dictionary teaches it names and domain terms.

## Account and licensing

Typeless requires an account. A free tier is available with a weekly word allowance; unlimited use is a paid subscription. This package installs the application only - it does not include or provide a subscription.

## This is a community-maintained package

This package downloads the official Typeless installer directly from the vendor's servers. It is **not** affiliated with or endorsed by Typeless. "Typeless" is a trademark of its respective owner.</description>
